Why not choose our hostel, which is located in the very center of Kyiv and has a modern kitchen, ergonomic orthopedic mattresses and a friendly team?

Our room #2 for 6 people is located on Saksaganskoho Street, just a 10-minute walk from the University metro station and 15 minutes from the Leo Tolstoy Square metro station!

Our prices are very affordable:
UAH 150 per day,
UAH 600/800 per week,
1800/2000 UAH per month.

We have hot water, free Wi-Fi with YouTube access, lockers and daily wet cleaning. Our admins work 24/7 to ensure strict face control and clear work.

We do not charge a deposit or commission because we provide services without an advance or utility payments. Check-in is quick and easy - we only need your passport.
